[SPEAKER_08] Četvrto radosno tajstvo

566
00:17:06,960 --> 00:17:09,960
[SPEAKER_08] koga si djevice u hramu prikazala.

567
00:17:09,960 --> 00:17:14,960
[SPEAKER_08] A sve se od hrama počinje.

568
00:17:14,960 --> 00:17:17,960
[SPEAKER_08] Hram presvetog trojstva

569
00:17:17,960 --> 00:17:21,960
[SPEAKER_08] i u hramu se opet odvija.

570
00:17:21,960 --> 00:17:24,960
[SPEAKER_08] Tako je i naša kršćanska,

571
00:17:24,960 --> 00:17:26,960
[SPEAKER_08] ne da mi moramo,

572
00:17:26,960 --> 00:17:28,960
[SPEAKER_08] nego znamo da je u hramu

573
00:17:28,960 --> 00:17:32,960
[SPEAKER_08] u istinu mjesto Božijeg počivališta

574
00:17:32,960 --> 00:17:33,960
[SPEAKER_08] i susreta.

575
00:17:33,960 --> 00:17:37,960
[SPEAKER_08] Pa neka evo i ovaj naš sada hod

576
00:17:37,960 --> 00:17:42,960
[SPEAKER_08] prema jednoj novoj modernoj kapeli

577
00:17:42,960 --> 00:17:44,960
[SPEAKER_08] svete majke Terezije,

578
00:17:44,960 --> 00:17:48,960
[SPEAKER_08] ali je hram i tamo ćemo mi ako Bog da slaviti.

579
00:17:48,960 --> 00:17:51,960
[SPEAKER_08] Neka nas bila ona susretne

580
00:17:51,960 --> 00:17:55,960
[SPEAKER_08] i da nađemo gospodina.

581
00:17:55,960 --> 00:17:58,960
[SPEAKER_04] Oče naš ko jesi na nebesima,

