773
00:22:06,960 --> 00:22:11,960
[SPEAKER_08] Sad se nalazimo vrlo blizu tom staroj čarši,

774
00:22:11,960 --> 00:22:14,960
[SPEAKER_08] koja je evo ispred nas,

775
00:22:14,960 --> 00:22:16,960
