00:22:20,960 --> 00:22:22,960
[SPEAKER_08] iza onoga,

779
00:22:22,960 --> 00:22:23,960
[SPEAKER_08] stabala viseta,

780
00:22:23,960 --> 00:22:25,960
[SPEAKER_08] u jedna kapelica naša,

781
00:22:25,960 --> 00:22:27,960
[SPEAKER_08] koja je bila,

782
00:22:27,960 --> 00:22:28,960
[SPEAKER_08] prije,

783
00:22:28,960 --> 00:22:31,960
[SPEAKER_08] bila stara mala crkva,

784
00:22:31,960 --> 00:22:35,960
[SPEAKER_08] gdje su Isusovci živjeli i radili,

785
00:22:35,960 --> 00:22:37,960
[SPEAKER_08] u vrijeme majke Terezije.

786
00:22:37,960 --> 00:22:39,960
[SPEAKER_08] Dakle,

787
00:22:39,960 --> 00:22:43,960
[SPEAKER_08] onda je potres to srušio,

788
00:22:43,960 --> 00:22:47,960
[SPEAKER_08] ali je Njemački karitas napravio barake,

789
00:22:47,960 --> 00:22:52,960
[SPEAKER_08] i sada imamo tu svake srijede sve tu misu,

790
00:22:52,960 --> 00:22:58,960
[SPEAKER_08] a tu je u jednoj baraci možda dvanesta kvadrata,

791
00:22:58,960 --> 00:23:01,960
[SPEAKER_08] jedni Franjo i Monika,

792
00:23:01,960 --> 00:23:04,960
[SPEAKER_08] podigli sedmero djece.

793
00:23:04,960 --> 00:23:07,960
[SPEAKER_08] Dakle, to su bile ovako,

794
00:23:07,960 --> 00:23:11,960
