798
00:23:31,960 --> 00:23:33,960
[SPEAKER_08] je, je.

799
00:23:33,960 --> 00:23:39,960
[SPEAKER_08] Danas je to većinski živan muslimanski,

800
00:23:39,960 --> 00:23:44,960
