802
00:23:49,960 --> 00:23:51,960
[SPEAKER_08] Evo, idemo dalje,

803
00:23:51,960 --> 00:23:53,960
[SPEAKER_08] te je to radosno otajstvo,

804
00:23:53,960 --> 00:23:56,960
[SPEAKER_08] koga si djevice u hramu našla.

805
00:23:56,960 --> 00:24:03,960
[SPEAKER_08] Evo, u hramu smo rekli da je počelo,

