00:29:50,960 --> 00:29:52,960
[SPEAKER_08] i blagoslovljen ti među ženama,

983
00:29:52,960 --> 00:29:56,960
[SPEAKER_08] prati ispovijest vjere Hrvata Katolika,

984
00:29:56,960 --> 00:30:00,960
[SPEAKER_08] čvrsto vjerujem u Boga, Oca,

985
00:30:00,960 --> 00:30:04,960
