986
00:30:04,960 --> 00:30:06,960
[SPEAKER_08] životom želim potvrditi

987
00:30:06,960 --> 00:30:10,960
[SPEAKER_06] krsti sade,

988
00:30:10,960 --> 00:30:12,960
[SPEAKER_07] tako obnoviti

989
00:30:12,960 --> 00:30:14,960
[SPEAKER_07] sveti pravjednosti

990
00:30:14,960 --> 00:30:16,960
[SPEAKER_07] i zade vjere

991
00:30:16,960 --> 00:30:18,960
[SPEAKER_07] i Isusa Krista,

992
00:30:18,960 --> 00:30:21,960
[SPEAKER_07] i vjernosti Katolikovi svoj crdi,

993
00:30:21,960 --> 00:30:24,960
[SPEAKER_07] svoju odluku polaše,

994
00:30:24,960 --> 00:30:26,960
[SPEAKER_07] i vežnešno srce,

995
00:30:26,960 --> 00:30:30,960
[SPEAKER_07] presvjetne dobrojnice Marijeva.

996
00:30:30,960 --> 00:30:33,960
[SPEAKER_00] Odvjetnice,

997
00:30:33,960 --> 00:30:35,960
[SPEAKER_00] na graninku stoj,

998
00:30:35,960 --> 00:30:38,960
[SPEAKER_00] čuvaj našu svetu vjeru

999
00:30:38,960 --> 00:30:40,960
[SPEAKER_00] i trvarski dom.

1000
00:30:40,960 --> 00:30:42,960
[SPEAKER_09] Dragi paterinko,

1001
00:30:42,960 --> 00:30:44,960
[SPEAKER_09] možete li vi nama samo, evo, ukratko reći,

1002
00:30:44,960 --> 00:30:47,960
[SPEAKER_09] vi ste ovdje župnik u katedrali,

1003
00:30:47,960 --> 00:30:48,960
[SPEAKER_09] nedavno ste došli,

1004
00:30:48,960 --> 00:30:50,960
[SPEAKER_09] pa nam možete samo dvije, tri riječi reći

1005
00:30:50,960 --> 00:30:51,960
[SPEAKER_09] malo samo o katedrali,

1006
00:30:51,960 --> 00:30:54,960
[SPEAKER_09] i vašem evo djelovanju ovdje u Makedoniji.

1007
00:30:54,960 --> 00:30:58,960
[SPEAKER_08] Katedrala je presvetan srcu Isusovu posvećena,

1008
00:30:58,960 --> 00:31:02,960
[SPEAKER_08] a inače sad se nalazimo uz crkvu Bogorodičinu,

1009
00:31:02,960 --> 00:31:06,960
[SPEAKER_08] hram pored kojega ćemo sada proći,

1010
00:31:06,960 --> 00:31:12,960
[SPEAKER_08] koji je jedno vrijeme bio i stolna crkva pravoslavnog biskupa,

1011
00:31:12,960 --> 00:31:18,960
[SPEAKER_08] a crkva katolička u Skoplju je živa,

1012
00:31:18,960 --> 00:31:19,960
[SPEAKER_08] malena,

1013
00:31:19,960 --> 00:31:24,960
[SPEAKER_08] a, evo, vidjet ćete ako Bog da ovaj prelijepu katedralu,

1014
00:31:24,960 --> 00:31:30,960
[SPEAKER_08] i u njoj jedine orgulje koje imaju u Makedoniji,

1015
00:31:30,960 --> 00:31:36,960
[SPEAKER_08] za koje se nadamo i u ovih dana dobiti potporu Hrvatske za štimavanje,

1016
00:31:36,960 --> 00:31:48,960
[SPEAKER_08] a zajednica je velim malena, ali vrlo, vrlo radosna i zna se radovati, slaviti.

1017
00:31:48,960 --> 00:32:09,960
[SPEAKER_08] Hrvatske smo proslavili 50 godina redogništva jedne časne i 24 godine biskupa Kire Stojanova i baš i bila ovaj prelijepa svećanost, pa se nadamo i vjerujemo da će tako biti i ove dvije večeri zajedno s vama.

1018
00:32:09,960 --> 00:32:15,960
